  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nIn some cases it is useful to add a set of trusted peers that avoid the scoring system (or always have the most positive score). This should be added as a CLI param. Peers that are considered trusted, do not get penalized in the scoring system and we therefore don't disconnect from them based on their behaviour. ",
